## Node and corridor coverage

First, here is the raw node and corridor coverage according to the draft district plans for each of the LRT stations.
Avonmore is one of the least covered, but is by no means alone.
Centre city is the driving factor of the high coverage rates of many stations.
Moving down the list, we can see that stations outside of downtown are generally not covered as much by nodes and corridors. 

